data.description: Back on market at no fault of the seller! Could it be that this home was meant for you? Are you tired of renting and ready to move quickly? Here's your opportunity! This unique, well-loved bungalow features a large front porch, 4 bedrooms  (2 on the first floor and 2 on the second floor), 2.5 bathrooms, open concept from the kitchen to living room, nice backyard and a bonus detached garage studio with full bathroom in the rear (sold as-is).  This home is also a 3 minute drive to beautiful water views on Chesapeake Ave.  Convenient access to the interstates for an easy commute throughout Hampton Roads.
